data.description: A place at the beach!!  Folly Beach!!  Close to everything Folly offers!!  Four bedroom home with pool as built can be used by one or two families!  Plus, two-family zoning means you can build a new house & keep the old!  Or use the existing home for income, while you design two new houses!  Up to 3,600 sq. ft. in total size, two detached homes are allowed here.  Survey and existing floor plans attached.  Good long-term rental income potential as built makes this a great way to get onto Folly now, while planning what to do here in the future!  New construction is everywhere!  Come be a part of Folly's next chapter!!
